"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/38/13928?source=related_link\">",
"      Pathophysiology of reflux esophagitis",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
