"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/62/12266/contributors\">",
"     Gordon M Saperia, MD, FACC",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
